            "Hand hygiene is done by using 60-95% alcohol-based hand sanitizer or by washing hands with soap and water for at least 20 seconds."=>"% 60-95 alkol bazlı el antiseptiği kullanarak veya en az 20 saniye boyunca elleri sabun ve suyla yıkayarak el hijyeni yapılmaktadır.",
